## **Key Legal Expressions to Master**

**‚ÄúIt depends on the circumstances of the case‚Äù**

- Typical legal thinking
- Most things are judged contextually

**‚ÄúIn principle‚Ä¶ but there are exceptions‚Äù**

- Standard legal qualification

**‚ÄúBalance‚Äù**

- THE key word in criminal law
- Always balancing competing interests

