## **SLIM STOMPER - AI Learning Tool**

### **Purpose:**

Help students memorize ECtHR case law effectively using smart flashcard system

### **How It Works:**

1. Presents questions about cases (multiple choice or fill-in)
1. **Adaptive learning:** If you struggle with a question, it will reappear
1. Practice weekly as you learn new cases
1. When you complete lessons successfully ‚Üí earn a ‚Äúcrown‚Äù

### **Benefits:**

- Based on scientific psychological research
- Proven to improve grades (from 6 ‚Üí 8, or 8 ‚Üí 10)
- Efficient brain training
- Free access

### **Where to Find:**

Brightspace ‚Üí Tools ‚Üí Slim Stomper

### **Important Cases to Memorize:**

Approximately 20-21 key cases throughout the course

### **Best Practice:**

Use Slim Stomper **alongside** (not instead of):

- Reading actual cases (builds reading skills)
- Watching web videos (understanding context)

